Aim:
To find the sum of digits of a given number using a loop.

Algorithm:
Start
Input number n
Initialize sum = 0
Repeat while n > 0
digit = n % 10
sum = sum + digit
n = n / 10
Print sum
Stop

Program:
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int n, sum = 0, digit;
    cout<<"Enter a number: ";
    cin>>n;

    while(n > 0){
        digit = n % 10;
        sum += digit;
        n /= 10;
    }

    cout<<"Sum of digits = "<<sum;
    return 0;
}

Sample Output:
Enter a number: 123
Sum of digits = 6

Result:
The program finds the sum of digits of the given number.

